analysis.Summary: This file defines a single-file Vue component that renders the Dribbble logo as an inline SVG graphic.
analysis.Purpose: To provide a reusable, presentational Dribbble social icon component within the project's icon set.

Components.name: DribbbleIcon
Components.responsibility: Encapsulates and renders the SVG markup for the Dribbble logo

analysis.Usage: Import the component (e.g. `import DribbbleIcon from 'modules/icons/socials/dribbble.vue'`) and register it locally or globally to include `<DribbbleIcon/>` in other Vue templates.
